          <title>Ohtani wins unanimous MVP after historic first season with Dodgers</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Los Angeles Dodgers' superstar Shohei Ohtani is the 2024 National League Most Valuable Player. It was a unanimous decision to award the Japanese phenom the 2024 MVP, and in doing so, create another historic moment as he becomes the first full-time designated hitter to win it.]]></description>
